From: Copilot <noreply@github.com>
Subject: [PATCH] lib: use libjpeg-62 bundled code when libjpeg-turbo is present

libjpeg-turbo reports JPEG_VERSION=80 for API compatibility but removes
internal struct fields (min_DCT_v_scaled_size, min_DCT_h_scaled_size,
jpeg_width, jpeg_height) that the bundled libjpeg-80 sources reference.
Map version 80 to the libjpeg-62 bundled code which uses the stable
public API and is compatible with libjpeg-turbo.

--- a/lib/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/lib/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -10,7 +10,8 @@ if (${JPEG_VERSION} LESS 80)
 endif()
 
 if (${JPEG_VERSION} EQUAL 80)
-    set(GV_JPEG_DIR libjpeg-80)
+    # libjpeg-turbo lacks min_DCT_{v,h}_scaled_size; use stable 6.2 code
+    set(GV_JPEG_DIR libjpeg-62)
 endif()
 
 if (${JPEG_VERSION} EQUAL 90)
